BetterPMMP
==========

BetterPMMP is a continuation and derivative work of PocketMine-MP, a server
software for Minecraft: Bedrock Edition. It exists to keep the PocketMine-MP
codebase maintained after the upstream project was archived.

Upstream project : PocketMine-MP  <https://github.com/pmmp/PocketMine-MP>
Based on         : PocketMine-MP 5.44.3
This distribution: 2026


