Notice of modifications (LGPL-3.0 / GPL-3.0 section 5a)
------------------------------------------------------

This is a modified version of PocketMine-MP. It has been changed from the
original PocketMine-MP 5.44.3 source by the BetterPMMP project in 2026. Source
files modified or added by BetterPMMP are marked in-line with the tag
[BetterPMMP-PATCH]. The complete corresponding source code is included in the
source/ directory of this distribution.


Third-party components
----------------------

The source/vendor/ directory contains third-party libraries, each distributed
under its own license as stated in that library's own LICENSE file, which is
retained unmodified.

One of those libraries is modified by BetterPMMP:

  source/vendor/pocketmine/raklib/src/server/Server.php

It is changed to slice the inter-tick sleep of the RakLib thread so that
outbound packet batches are picked up within about a millisecond instead of up
to a full 10 ms tick. The change is marked in-line with [BetterPMMP-PATCH], and
the same diff is kept in source/build/betterpmmp-vendor-patches/ because a
composer install or update overwrites the vendor tree and reverts it. RakLib is
distributed under the GPL-3.0 with the exception stated in its own LICENSE.md,
which is retained unmodified.

The source/bin/ directory contains a build of PHP together with its extensions
and supporting libraries, distributed under the PHP License v3.01 and the
respective licenses of the bundled components. See source/bin/php/license.txt.


